<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="zh-Hant">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8" />
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
<title>iFanzy 創作者 - 你的AI分身在你睡覺時工作</title>
<style>
:root {
  --bg:#0a0a0a;
  --panel:#151515;
  --yellow:#ffc61a;
  --yellow-glow:#ffdb4d;
  --white:#ffffff;
  --gray:#b4b4b4;
  --muted:#767676;
  --line:rgba(255,255,255,.11);
}
* { box-sizing:border-box; margin:0; padding:0; }
html { scroll-snap-type:y mandatory; scroll-behavior:smooth; }
body {
  background:var(--bg); color:var(--white);
  font-family:Inter,-apple-system,BlinkMacSystemFont,"SF Pro Display",sans-serif;
  overflow-x:hidden; -webkit-font-smoothing:antialiased;
}

/* Enhanced background with texture */
.slide {
  position:relative; width:100vw; height:100vh; min-height:100vh;
  padding:0; scroll-snap-align:start; overflow:hidden;
  background:
    radial-gradient(circle at 75% 20%, rgba(255,198,26,.15), transparent 35%),
    radial-gradient(circle at 25% 80%, rgba(255,198,26,.08), transparent 40%),
    var(--bg);
}
.slide:before {
  content:""; position:absolute; inset:0; pointer-events:none; z-index:1;
  background-image:
    linear-gradient(rgba(255,255,255,.018) 1px, transparent 1px),
    linear-gradient(90deg, rgba(255,255,255,.018) 1px, transparent 1px);
  background-size:64px 64px;
  mask-image:
    radial-gradient(ellipse 90% 60% at 50% 20%, rgba(0,0,0,.8), transparent 85%),
    linear-gradient(to bottom, rgba(0,0,0,.6), transparent 90%);
  mask-composite:intersect;
}
.slide:after {
  content:""; position:absolute; inset:0; pointer-events:none; z-index:0;
  background:
    radial-gradient(circle at 50% 0%, rgba(255,198,26,.06), transparent 45%);
  opacity:.6;
}

/* Brand mark */
.wordmark {
  position:fixed; left:clamp(32px,5vw,80px); top:clamp(32px,4vh,56px); z-index:100;
  font-size:clamp(22px,2.2vw,32px); font-weight:900;
  letter-spacing:-.04em; color:var(--yellow);
  text-shadow:0 0 40px rgba(255,198,26,.4);
}

/* Language switcher */
.lang-switcher {
  position:fixed; right:clamp(32px,5vw,80px); top:clamp(32px,4vh,56px); z-index:100;
  display:flex; gap:12px; align-items:center;
}
.lang-btn {
  padding:10px 18px;
  background:linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(255,255,255,.08), rgba(255,255,255,.03));
  border:1px solid rgba(255,255,255,.12);
  border-radius:8px;
  color:var(--gray);
  font-size:14px;
  font-weight:600;
  cursor:pointer;
  transition:all .3s;
  text-decoration:none;
  backdrop-filter:blur(12px);
}
.lang-btn:hover {
  background:linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(255,255,255,.12), rgba(255,255,255,.06));
  border-color:rgba(255,198,26,.3);
  color:var(--white);
  transform:translateY(-2px);
}
.lang-btn.active {
  background:linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(255,198,26,.15), rgba(255,198,26,.08));
  border-color:rgba(255,198,26,.4);
  color:var(--yellow);
  box-shadow:0 0 20px rgba(255,198,26,.2);
}

/* Content container with proper centering */
.content {
  position:relative; z-index:2;
  min-height:100vh;
  display:flex; flex-direction:column; justify-content:center;
  padding:clamp(80px,12vh,140px) clamp(32px,6vw,100px) clamp(80px,10vh,120px);
  max-width:1600px; margin:0 auto;
}
.content.center { text-align:center; align-items:center; }

/* Typography with better spacing */
.kicker {
  color:var(--yellow); font-size:clamp(11px,1.1vw,13px);
  font-weight:850; letter-spacing:.2em; text-transform:uppercase;
  margin-bottom:clamp(20px,2.5vh,32px);
  opacity:.95;
}
h1 {
  margin:0; font-size:clamp(56px,7vw,98px);
  line-height:1.25; letter-spacing:-.02em; font-weight:900;
  text-shadow:0 2px 40px rgba(0,0,0,.5);
}
h2 {
  margin:0; font-size:clamp(42px,5.2vw,72px);
  line-height:1.3; letter-spacing:-.018em; font-weight:880;
  text-shadow:0 2px 30px rgba(0,0,0,.4);
}
h3 {
  margin:0; font-size:clamp(20px,2vw,28px);
  line-height:1.35; letter-spacing:-.02em; font-weight:700;
}
p {
  margin:0; color:var(--gray);
  font-size:clamp(18px,1.8vw,22px);
  line-height:1.55; letter-spacing:-.01em;
}
.small { color:var(--muted); font-size:clamp(14px,1.4vw,17px); line-height:1.6; }
.yellow { color:var(--yellow); }
.accent {
  width:clamp(60px,8vw,80px); height:4px; border-radius:999px;
  background:linear-gradient(90deg, var(--yellow), var(--yellow-glow));
  margin:clamp(28px,3.5vh,40px) auto 0;
  box-shadow:0 0 20px rgba(255,198,26,.5);
}
.tagline {
  font-size:clamp(20px,2.2vw,26px); color:var(--gray);
  margin-top:clamp(24px,3vh,36px); max-width:clamp(600px,60vw,920px);
  line-height:1.5; letter-spacing:-.015em;
}

/* Premium button */
.btn {
  display:inline-flex; align-items:center; gap:12px;
  padding:clamp(16px,2vh,22px) clamp(32px,4vw,48px);
  border-radius:999px;
  background:linear-gradient(135deg, var(--yellow) 0%, var(--yellow-glow) 100%);
  color:#0a0a0a;
  font-size:clamp(15px,1.6vw,18px); font-weight:800;
  letter-spacing:-.015em;
  border:0; cursor:pointer;
  text-decoration:none;
  position:relative; overflow:hidden;
  box-shadow:
    0 1px 0 rgba(255,255,255,.3) inset,
    0 8px 24px rgba(255,198,26,.35),
    0 16px 48px rgba(255,198,26,.2);
  transition:all .4s cubic-bezier(.22,.61,.36,1);
}
.btn:before {
  content:""; position:absolute; inset:0;
  background:linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(255,255,255,.2), transparent 60%);
  opacity:0; transition:opacity .3s;
}
.btn:hover {
  transform:translateY(-3px) scale(1.02);
  box-shadow:
    0 1px 0 rgba(255,255,255,.4) inset,
    0 12px 32px rgba(255,198,26,.45),
    0 24px 64px rgba(255,198,26,.25);
}
.btn:hover:before { opacity:1; }

/* Layout grids */
.two {
  display:grid;
  grid-template-columns:1.05fr .95fr;
  gap:clamp(40px,6vw,80px);
  align-items:center;
}
.card-grid {
  display:grid;
  grid-template-columns:repeat(4,1fr);
  gap:clamp(16px,2vw,24px);
  margin-top:clamp(48px,6vh,72px);
}
.card-grid.three { grid-template-columns:repeat(3,1fr); }
.card-grid.two { grid-template-columns:repeat(2,1fr); gap:clamp(20px,3vw,32px); }

/* Premium cards with enhanced depth */
.card {
  min-height:clamp(180px,22vh,220px);
  border:1px solid rgba(255,255,255,.14);
  background:
    linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(255,255,255,.09) 0%, rgba(255,255,255,.03) 100%);
  border-radius:clamp(28px,3.5vw,36px);
  padding:clamp(36px,4.5vw,48px) clamp(28px,3.5vw,38px);
  backdrop-filter:blur(28px) saturate(190%);
  position:relative; overflow:hidden;
  transition:all .5s cubic-bezier(.22,.61,.36,1);
  box-shadow:
    0 1px 0 rgba(255,255,255,.1) inset,
    0 12px 40px rgba(0,0,0,.5),
    0 2px 4px rgba(0,0,0,.25);
  text-align:center;
}
.card:before {
  content:""; position:absolute; inset:0;
  background:
    radial-gradient(circle at 50% 0%, rgba(255,198,26,.1), transparent 70%);
  opacity:0; transition:opacity .4s;
}
.card h3 {
  font-size:clamp(26px,3vw,42px);
  font-weight:900;
  line-height:1.1;
  letter-spacing:-.035em;
  margin-bottom:clamp(16px,2vh,24px);
  background:linear-gradient(135deg, var(--white) 0%, var(--gray) 100%);
  -webkit-background-clip:text; -webkit-text-fill-color:transparent;
  background-clip:text;
  word-wrap:break-word;
  overflow-wrap:break-word;
}
.card p {
  font-size:clamp(16px,1.7vw,20px);
  line-height:1.6;
  color:#a8a8a8;
  letter-spacing:-.01em;
}
.card:hover {
  transform:translateY(-8px) scale(1.015);
  border-color:rgba(255,198,26,.25);
  box-shadow:
    0 1px 0 rgba(255,255,255,.15) inset,
    0 20px 56px rgba(0,0,0,.6),
    0 0 0 1px rgba(255,198,26,.15),
    0 12px 40px rgba(255,198,26,.15);
}
.card:hover:before { opacity:1; }

/* Enhanced cards for feature-rich sections */
.card.enhanced {
  min-height:clamp(200px,24vh,240px);
  background:
    linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(255,255,255,.1) 0%, rgba(255,255,255,.035) 100%);
  border:1px solid rgba(255,255,255,.16);
  padding:clamp(38px,4.8vw,50px) clamp(32px,4vw,42px);
  box-shadow:
    0 1px 0 rgba(255,255,255,.12) inset,
    0 16px 48px rgba(0,0,0,.55),
    0 2px 6px rgba(0,0,0,.3);
}
.card.enhanced h3 {
  font-size:clamp(24px,2.6vw,34px);
  margin-bottom:clamp(16px,2vh,22px);
  font-weight:800;
}
.card.enhanced p {
  font-size:clamp(16px,1.7vw,19px);
  line-height:1.7;
  color:#b0b0b0;
}
.card.enhanced:hover {
  transform:translateY(-10px) scale(1.02);
  box-shadow:
    0 1px 0 rgba(255,255,255,.18) inset,
    0 24px 64px rgba(0,0,0,.65),
    0 0 0 1px rgba(255,198,26,.25),
    0 16px 48px rgba(255,198,26,.2);
}
.card:before {
  content:""; position:absolute; inset:0;
  background:
    radial-gradient(circle at 50% 0%, rgba(255,198,26,.12), transparent 60%);
  opacity:0; transition:opacity .4s;
}
.card:after {
  content:""; position:absolute; top:0; left:0; right:0; height:1px;
  background:linear-gradient(90deg, transparent, rgba(255,255,255,.2), transparent);
  opacity:0; transition:opacity .4s;
}
.card:hover {
  transform:translateY(-6px) scale(1.01);
  border-color:rgba(255,198,26,.3);
  box-shadow:
    0 1px 0 rgba(255,255,255,.12) inset,
    0 16px 48px rgba(0,0,0,.5),
    0 0 0 1px rgba(255,198,26,.15),
    0 8px 32px rgba(255,198,26,.15);
}
.card:hover:before { opacity:1; }
.card:hover:after { opacity:1; }
.card h3 { margin-bottom:12px; }
.card p { font-size:clamp(15px,1.5vw,17px); color:#a0a0a0; line-height:1.6; }

/* Icon box with glow */
.icon-box {
  width:clamp(44px,5vw,52px); height:clamp(44px,5vw,52px);
  border-radius:clamp(14px,2vw,18px);
  border:1px solid rgba(255,198,26,.4);
  background:
    linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(255,198,26,.15), rgba(255,198,26,.05));
  display:grid; place-items:center; color:var(--yellow);
  margin-bottom:clamp(20px,2.5vh,28px);
  font-weight:850; font-size:clamp(20px,2.2vw,26px);
  box-shadow:
    0 0 24px rgba(255,198,26,.2),
    0 1px 0 rgba(255,255,255,.1) inset;
  position:relative;
}
.icon-box:before {
  content:""; position:absolute; inset:-2px;
  background:linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(255,198,26,.3), transparent);
  border-radius:inherit; z-index:-1; opacity:0;
  transition:opacity .3s;
}
.card:hover .icon-box:before { opacity:1; }

/* Flow steps with premium style */
.flow {
  display:grid;
  grid-template-columns:repeat(7,1fr);
  gap:clamp(12px,1.5vw,16px);
  margin-top:clamp(40px,5vh,60px);
}
.step {
  border:1px solid rgba(255,255,255,.11);
  background:
    linear-gradient(145deg, rgba(255,255,255,.06), rgba(255,255,255,.02));
  border-radius:clamp(20px,2.5vw,28px);
  padding:clamp(20px,2.5vw,28px) clamp(16px,2vw,22px);
  min-height:clamp(140px,18vh,180px);
  position:relative; overflow:hidden;
  backdrop-filter:blur(12px);
  transition:all .4s cubic-bezier(.22,.61,.36,1);
  box-shadow:0 4px 16px rgba(0,0,0,.3);
}
.step:before {
  content:""; position:absolute; inset:0;
  background:radial-gradient(circle at 50% 0%, rgba(255,198,26,.08), transparent 70%);
  opacity:0; transition:opacity .3s;
}
.step:hover {
  transform:translateY(-4px);
  border-color:rgba(255,198,26,.25);
  box-shadow:
    0 8px 24px rgba(0,0,0,.4),
    0 0 0 1px rgba(255,198,26,.1);
}
.step:hover:before { opacity:1; }
.step .num {
  color:var(--yellow); font-size:clamp(11px,1.2vw,13px);
  font-weight:900; letter-spacing:.12em;
  margin-bottom:clamp(16px,2vh,20px);
  text-shadow:0 0 12px rgba(255,198,26,.5);
}
.step h3 { font-size:clamp(18px,2vw,22px); margin-bottom:clamp(8px,1vh,12px); }
.step p { font-size:clamp(13px,1.4vw,15px); line-height:1.5; color:var(--muted); }

/* Big number with premium effect */
.big-number {
  color:var(--yellow);
  font-size:clamp(120px,18vw,240px);
  line-height:.8; letter-spacing:-.08em; font-weight:900;
  background:linear-gradient(135deg, var(--yellow) 0%, var(--yellow-glow) 100%);
  -webkit-background-clip:text; -webkit-text-fill-color:transparent;
  background-clip:text;
  filter:drop-shadow(0 0 40px rgba(255,198,26,.3));
}

/* List with better spacing */
.list {
  display:flex; flex-direction:column;
  gap:clamp(16px,2vh,22px);
  margin-top:clamp(28px,3.5vh,40px);
}
.item {
  display:flex; gap:clamp(12px,1.5vw,16px); align-items:flex-start;
  font-size:clamp(18px,1.9vw,21px); color:#d0d0d0; line-height:1.45;
  letter-spacing:-.012em;
}
.item .mark {
  color:var(--yellow); font-weight:900; min-width:clamp(16px,2vw,20px);
  text-shadow:0 0 12px rgba(255,198,26,.4);
}

/* Premium panels */
.panel {
  border:1px solid rgba(255,255,255,.12);
  background:
    linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(255,255,255,.07) 0%, rgba(255,255,255,.025) 100%);
  border-radius:clamp(28px,3.5vw,40px);
  padding:clamp(32px,4vw,48px);
  min-height:clamp(340px,42vh,440px);
  position:relative; overflow:hidden;
  backdrop-filter:blur(24px) saturate(180%);
  box-shadow:
    0 1px 0 rgba(255,255,255,.08) inset,
    0 12px 40px rgba(0,0,0,.4);
  transition:all .4s cubic-bezier(.22,.61,.36,1);
}
.panel:before {
  content:""; position:absolute; top:0; left:0; right:0; height:2px;
  background:linear-gradient(90deg, transparent, rgba(255,255,255,.15), transparent);
}
.panel:hover {
  transform:translateY(-4px);
  border-color:rgba(255,198,26,.2);
  box-shadow:
    0 1px 0 rgba(255,255,255,.12) inset,
    0 16px 48px rgba(0,0,0,.5),
    0 0 0 1px rgba(255,198,26,.1);
}
.panel h3 {
  margin-bottom:clamp(24px,3vh,32px);
  font-size:clamp(26px,3vw,36px);
  letter-spacing:-.025em;
}
.compare {
  display:grid; grid-template-columns:1fr 1fr;
  gap:clamp(20px,3vw,32px);
  margin-top:clamp(40px,5vh,56px);
}

/* Responsive */
@media(max-width:1024px){
  .slide { min-height:900px; }
  .two, .compare { grid-template-columns:1fr; gap:clamp(32px,5vh,48px); }
  .card-grid, .flow { grid-template-columns:1fr 1fr; }
}
@media(max-width:640px){
  .card-grid, .flow { grid-template-columns:1fr; }
  .wordmark { font-size:24px; left:24px; top:28px; }
}
</style>

</head>
<body>

<div class="wordmark">iFanzy</div>

<div class="lang-switcher">
<a href="creator_recruitment.html" class="lang-btn">EN</a>
<a href="creator_recruitment_tc.html" class="lang-btn active">繁中</a>
</div>

<!-- Slide 1: Hero -->
<section class="slide">
<div class="content center">
<div class="kicker">創作者AI分身</div>
<h1>你的AI分身<br/>在你睡覺時工作</h1>
<p class="tagline">
創建你的授權AI克隆，24/7聊天、直播、賺錢
</p>
<div class="accent"></div>
<div style="margin-top:clamp(48px,6vh,64px)">
<a href="#contact" class="btn">加入 iFanzy →</a>
</div>
</div>
</section>

<!-- Slide 2: 24小時困境 -->
<section class="slide">
<div class="content center">
<div class="kicker">24小時陷阱</div>
<h2>創作者的<br/><span class="yellow">不可能一天</span></h2>
<p class="tagline" style="margin-top:clamp(32px,4vh,48px);margin-bottom:clamp(48px,6vh,64px);max-width:800px">
你是一個人，卻有來自全球的數百萬粉絲。你如何應對？
</p>
<div class="card-grid">
<div class="card">
<h3>早上6點</h3>
<p>創作內容</p>
</div>
<div class="card">
<h3>上午10點</h3>
<p>回覆私訊</p>
</div>
<div class="card">
<h3>下午2點</h3>
<p>開會</p>
</div>
<div class="card">
<h3>晚上6點</h3>
<p>與粉絲互動</p>
</div>
<div class="card">
<h3>晚上10點</h3>
<p>直播</p>
</div>
<div class="card">
<h3>凌晨2點</h3>
<p>與亞洲粉絲聊天</p>
</div>
<div class="card">
<h3>早上6點</h3>
<p>重新開始...</p>
</div>
<div class="card" style="background:linear-gradient(135deg,rgba(255,198,26,.12),rgba(255,198,26,.04));border-color:rgba(255,198,26,.4)">
<h3 style="color:var(--yellow)">過勞</h3>
<p style="color:var(--gray)">你撐不下去了</p>
</div>
</div>
</div>
</section>

<!-- Slide 3: 瓶頸問題 -->
<section class="slide">
<div class="content center">
<div class="kicker">不可能的方程式</div>
<h2>24小時 × 24時區<br/>× <span class="yellow">∞ 粉絲</span></h2>
<div style="text-align:center;margin-top:clamp(56px,7vh,80px)">
<div class="big-number">24</div>
<p style="margin-top:clamp(24px,3vh,36px);font-size:clamp(22px,2.6vw,32px);color:var(--yellow);font-weight:700">
一天只有24小時
</p>
</div>
<p class="tagline" style="margin-top:clamp(48px,6vh,64px);font-size:clamp(20px,2.2vw,26px)">
當你睡覺時，你的粉絲正醒著。<br/>
他們想要你現在，而不是8小時後。
</p>
</div>
</section>

<!-- Slide 4: AI不取代你 -->
<section class="slide">
<div class="content">
<div class="two">
<div>
<div class="kicker">AI為你工作</div>
<h2>你的AI分身<br/><span class="yellow">不會取代你</span></h2>
<div class="list">
<div class="item"><span class="mark">✓</span> 你保持100%控制權</div>
<div class="item"><span class="mark">✓</span> AI處理重複性對話</div>
<div class="item"><span class="mark">✓</span> 你專注創作優質內容</div>
<div class="item"><span class="mark">✓</span> 粉絲24/7獲得即時回覆</div>
<div class="item"><span class="mark">✓</span> 你睡覺時也在賺錢</div>
</div>
</div>
<div style="text-align:center">
<p style="font-size:clamp(32px,4vw,56px);font-weight:900;line-height:1.2;margin-bottom:clamp(32px,4vh,48px)">
你 + <span class="yellow">AI分身</span>
</p>
<p style="font-size:clamp(18px,2vw,24px);color:var(--gray);line-height:1.6">
你的AI為你工作，<br/>而不是代替你
</p>
</div>
</div>
</div>
</section>

<!-- Slide 5: 5步流程 -->
<section class="slide">
<div class="content center">
<div class="kicker">如何運作</div>
<h2>用 <span class="yellow">5步</span><br/>創建你的AI分身</h2>
<div class="flow" style="grid-template-columns:repeat(5,1fr);margin-top:clamp(56px,7vh,80px)">
<div class="step">
<div class="num">步驟 1</div>
<h3>上傳內容</h3>
<p>分享你的影片、聊天、個性</p>
</div>
<div class="step">
<div class="num">步驟 2</div>
<h3>AI訓練</h3>
<p>AI學習你的聲音和風格</p>
</div>
<div class="step">
<div class="num">步驟 3</div>
<h3>你審核</h3>
<p>測試並批准你的AI分身</p>
</div>
<div class="step">
<div class="num">步驟 4</div>
<h3>設定界限</h3>
